snippet.title: Starri - Find your rhythm - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Bringing you a new music motion game to experience your favorite artists and music in an unrivaled multi-sensory way.

Download now on the app stores, and get immersed into the music you love: https://starri.app/find-your-rhythm

Tell us if you love it in a comment!

#starri #motiongame #musicgame #mobilegame
